description: AMUNDI MSCI WORLD EX EUROPE UCITS ETF seeks to replicate as closely as possible the performance of the MSCI World ex Europe Index, whether the trend is rising or falling. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to around 1200 stocks worldwide with a single transaction. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi MSCI World Ex Europe UCITS ETF - EUR (C)
